---

## Handoff

### Result

Implemented in full. Key changes:

- **`src/burnt/core/models.py`**: `estimated_dbu` is now `float | None`; `confidence` literal extended with `"none"`; all display methods (`comparison_table`, `_to_html_table`, `to_markdown`, `__repr__`) guard `None` fields and append the doctor hint when `confidence == "none"`.
- **`src/burnt/estimators/pipeline.py`**: offline branch returns `model_copy` nulling all cost fields with `confidence="none"` while preserving `breakdown` (complexity) and `warnings`; connected-mode path now computes `estimated_cost_usd` from `estimated_dbu` via `get_dbu_rate(cluster.sku)` (fixing the gap where `HybridEstimator` always returned `estimated_cost_usd=None`).
- **`src/burnt/__init__.py`**: `estimate()` `currency` parameter now defaults to `get_default_currency()` (wiring up the s2-09 default currency system).
- **`src/burnt/cli/main.py`**: `check` command extended to accept inline SQL — if the argument is not a valid path, `_check_inline_sql()` runs anti-pattern detection + complexity scoring and prints the offline format.
- **`tests/unit/estimators/test_pipeline.py`** and **`tests/unit/test_api.py`**: offline assertions updated; new tests for `confidence=="none"`, preserved complexity, and connected-mode cost population.

500 unit tests pass. `ruff check src/` clean.

